    "name": "《蜀山：初章》online",
    "steam_appid": 2375330,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《蜀山：初章》网络版是一款由重楼工作室研发的最新国产端游。故事以还珠楼主的《蜀山剑侠传》为大背景，发生在其之后千年灵气复苏之时，包含有：无缝地图、特色修仙、领土国战、飞行贸易、肉鸽搭配等诸多开放好玩的国风元素 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【修仙世界 上天入海】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.当前可以御剑横空、瞬息千里；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.当前可以水底探索、也可以在浅水、水面等区域战斗；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.后续资料片将开放空战、水战，包括：北海陷空岛、东海紫云宫等大型资料片玩法</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/e4f3cad3b0c9a2cbb7b6a87e1f340a7e.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/e4f3cad3b0c9a2cbb7b6a87e1f340a7e.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/e4f3cad3b0c9a2cbb7b6a87e1f340a7e.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【肉鸽搭配 百炼千仙】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.【仙道灵根】：五行或雷、冰；天灵根或伪灵根；什么是你走上仙道巅峰的凭依</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.【奇遇天赋】：初生不凡，探索大千中去搭配独有天赋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.【飞升境界】：凡人修仙，渡劫筑基，一步一重天</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.【绝世功法】：以功法为核心Build你唯一仙途</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5.【神兵词条】：不卖数值不氪金！神兵词条全靠刷刷刷！数百Build体系</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6.【自由传承】：十大流派，上千技能！专精或博采众长，随心而定！（当前已开放四大流派300多可收集切换技能）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7.【法宝神通】：独有Build倾向，可瞬时改变战局！也是炼妖飞行的本命核心</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/cb265cc42041cbf70ff8529ed7b62c15.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/cb265cc42041cbf70ff8529ed7b62c15.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/cb265cc42041cbf70ff8529ed7b62c15.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【修仙百艺 身份玩法】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.在蜀山的大世界里，道友可以自由的研究身份玩法：丹、兵、器、宝、物、阵法师、驯兽师、垂钓者、等身份玩法；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.当前已开放炼丹、炼宝等玩法相关；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/7b3c2652105bb34802208efb467ec51c.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/7b3c2652105bb34802208efb467ec51c.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/7b3c2652105bb34802208efb467ec51c.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【自由贸易 互通有无】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.寄卖行；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.摆摊；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/c62b2344b2629fd0f8609e7c6b99c7fa.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/c62b2344b2629fd0f8609e7c6b99c7fa.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/c62b2344b2629fd0f8609e7c6b99c7fa.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【无缝地图 畅爽PK】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.告别传统日常、副本网游，还原2005年前端游的感动</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.野外族群、野外首领；占地刷怪，包场BOSS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.从小规模遭遇战到大规模宗族门派约战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/960cc7ca1a4bea7557606868f79816af.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/960cc7ca1a4bea7557606868f79816af.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/960cc7ca1a4bea7557606868f79816af.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【宗族位面 建造征伐】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.以宗族为核心探索、踏上《蜀山：初章》修仙之旅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.开辟自己的独有的宗族位面，一起收集、建设自己独一无二的领土</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/b116a18ec97b13ca7c646e540d79ccb5.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/b116a18ec97b13ca7c646e540d79ccb5.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/b116a18ec97b13ca7c646e540d79ccb5.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/960cc7ca1a4bea7557606868f79816af.poster.avif?t=1769142312\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/960cc7ca1a4bea7557606868f79816af.webm?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2375330/extras/960cc7ca1a4bea7557606868f79816af.mp4?t=1769142312\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
